{"tid":1731284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大有難 萬方支援 刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-11-17T16:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T18:09:36.000Z","uid":194525,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32fea65ee54254d7810ac239f50853517a06f2ed","tid":1731284,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足不是Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n連方希望各大市民<span style=\"color: red;\">朝早6點</span>開花<br />\n入理大救手足既各位<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住帶美國國旗</span><br />\n我要見到旗海<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehykxfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehykxfC.jpg&h=aed30efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大目標<br />\n1.救出所有理工手足<br />\n2.針對狗宅 針對狗屋<br />\n3.針對『正苦』建築物<br />\n4.針對黨鐵 紅隧西隧<br />\n5.針對中資機構<br />\n<br />\n理大既手足頂住 <span style=\"color: red;\">美軍</span>嚟緊<br />\n冇錯講緊<span style=\"color: red;\">美軍</span> 捱多陣<span style=\"color: red;\">美軍</span>就殺到<br />\n到時為佢地引路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YB8Xztt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYB8Xztt.jpg&h=b554c09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到要光復這香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到依個po既所有手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">將以上黎明行動既所有內容copy&amp;paste share出去</span><br />\n1傳10 10傳100 100傳1000 1000傳10000<br />\n我地有200萬人 理工手足你地絕不孤單 頂住<br />\n<br />\n最後依個係連方既警告 <br />\n若香港綠曱甴開實彈鎮壓 香港人一定令到你地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冚家剷<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理大有難 萬方支援 刻不容緩</span><br />\n我要依個post長期置頂<br />\n朝早係最最最熱門post"},{"pid":"0afeda52d0fd03b4c74a73ea39888f71b968f843","tid":1731284,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8568e4714e31514a6a70122e4638365acc174cdf","tid":1731284,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"塞鐵塞路又搞鳩冇車低下層"},{"pid":"4ad07b7a265b50ac5972edb0ac79fdaae23b30eb","tid":1731284,"uid":148023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"和理非想救理大?<br />\n不妨睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1730983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1730983</a>"},{"pid":"c3adade15bddc94424a207f4f121e6f77506f112","tid":1731284,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"APSS鐘劍華教授願意返polyu 呼籲警方克制，但前提是有更多「同學」特別係理大生或舊生願意陪伴，令傳媒關注，請問大家是否願意陪伴，僅僅是回去作呼籲，可聯絡傳媒到場採訪。如有願意前往的，可pm 96322769 Ken莊，加大家入group。"},{"pid":"3051b0f68c8ea78f86d8e6c097158577f9280e45","tid":1731284,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"我要見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國國旗</span></span>"},{"pid":"1689fe7fd1f38d4c22ee1ae7b5cc1c33c468e34e","tid":1731284,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0903482ecae61b609d7f92da2ccc02eadc902852","tid":1731284,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2ae9116dda1c7fe474c5efada8d859ef540f719","tid":1731284,"uid":140850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"sir this way 今次嚟真"},{"pid":"9f9af329701a5027f95f4b42e307e3549f5ced64","tid":1731284,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2ae9116dda1c7fe474c5efada8d859ef540f719","tid":1731284,"uid":140850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"sir this way 今次嚟真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯 今次美軍真係來了<br />\n所以理工手足頂住 爲佢地引路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{